title: Worst Date Wednesday: She Invited 30 People on the Date
description: Jess has always struggled with understanding when guys were interested in her.  She tells us how she invited a bunch of people to hang out not realizing the guy had asked her out on a date, and how she friend-zoned her husband for years.
